Apple iPhone 4 Black 16GB

 

In working condition unlocked

(Have taken to Apple store to clear all data & all checked)

ready to use on any network

Auction contents:

·     Apple iPhone 4 16GB

·     Apple earphones with remote & Mic

·     Dock connector to USB cable

·     USB power adapter

·     Original box and packaging

·     BONUS ‘speck’ phone protective case – purple (picture looks blue)

 

Condition - See pictures for close up of item condition.

In excellent 'used' condition.  Phone works perfectly.  This belonged to my 10 year old son, so it wasn’t used a lot & was hardly taken out of the house!  I can’t find any scratches, or dints, it looks perfect to me.  Even the back of the phone is scratch free.  There is a surface protector on the phone, and my son had a phone case, which both have been there since we purchased the phone.  You can see some bubbling on the front of the phone, this is from the surface protector.  It doesn’t need to be replaced as you can still see the screen, but it is easily replaceable & cheap to do so!

I don’t keep my phones for a long time as I update them regularly. 

(as you can see I have other phones listed).

 

***please take the time to view my other items as I am having a huge clearance***

 

PAYMENT

Australian bidders: please pay by PayPal or direct bank deposit (my bank details will be shown at processing payment) Please include your eBay user ID so that I know whom the payment is from. The item will be posted once funds have been cleared.

International bidders: PayPal is accepted for international bidders.

POSTAGE

Within Australia: please see postage and payment section in the listing.  If you require registered post as well as insurance, please let me know & I will arrange a quote for you.  You can choose between regular mail and express post. 

International bidders: Shipping will be via airmail but please email me first for a postage quote to your country.
